experiment_run.description: This runs repeatable experiments on CrowdFlower every five hours.

mailman.description: This checks mailman@crowdflower.com for new messages and processes them.

debits_credits_report.description: Generate a partial monthly list of self service debits and credits and send to the DIY manager.

amt_check.description: Send us an email if we're running out of funds on Mechanical Turk.

rate_limit_report.description: This checks for any workers or IPs blocked by rate limiting and sends the report of those.

csvman.description: This updates reports that are out of date, because new judgments are available.

hit_verifier.description: This verifies HITs submitted by workers on mechanical turk to prevent scams.

debits_credits_monthly_report.description: Generate a full monthly report of self service debits and credits and send to the DIY manager.

new_users_report.description: Generate a list of new users and send to the DIY manager.

hit_purger.description: This purges old HITs from AMT.

expire_qualification_answers.description: Expire QualificationAnswers for standard qualifications that have expiration settings.

unfud_pivotal.description: This generates an XML file containing all open Unfuddle Tickets to be integrated with Pivotal Tracker.

navteq_report.description: This sends a summary count of units completed to Arvel for weekly invoicing

job_heartbeat.description: This makes sure all jobs are posted or taken down when needed.

experiment_orderer.description: This orders the repeatable experiments on CrowdFlower every 15 minutes.

margin_report.description: Generate a report of costs every day of the month at noon PST.
